.SH SYSTEM OPTIMIZATIONS

The setup script applies several system optimizations:

.TP
.B File Watcher Limits
Increases inotify file watchers for development tools (VS Code, webpack, etc.)

.TP
.B SSD Optimization
Enables fstrim timer for better SSD performance and longevity

.TP
.B Projects Directory
Creates ~/Projects for organizing code

.TP
.B Shell Aliases
